quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,12,"Uwo muriro ubabonye bakiri kure, baca bumva ishavu ryawo n’uguhinda kwawo"
  25,13,"Batawe muri uwo muriro udahera hakaba hari ahantu hatoyi cane nabo baboshwe, aho niho bazohamagara urupfu rubashikire"
  25,14,"Ntimuhamagare uno musi urupfu rumwe, ahubwo nimu hamagare amapfu menshi"
  25,15,"Vuga uti:- mbega ibi nivyo vyiza canke Ijuru ry’ubuzima budahera ryateguriwe abantu batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri kugira ngo bibe kuribo impembo nziza n’ingaruka nziza"
  25,16,"Bazoronswa muri ayo Majuru ivyo bipfuzamwo vyose hanyuma babeyo mubuzima bwabo bwose, kuko iyi niyo ndagano y’Umuremyi wawe ikenewe kurihwa"
  25,17,"Umusi Imana izobegeranya abo bahakanyi bayo, hamwe n’ababasenga aho bosenze Imana y’ukuri ninaho izovuga ibabwira iti:- mbega ni mwebwe mwatakaje aba bantu banje canke nibo bonyene bazimiye inzira kubwabo"
  25,18,"Nabo bazovuga bati:- Imana irisukuye nigabanukirwa ryivyarivyo vyose kandi ntibirekuriwe kuri twebwe kubagira ngo babe abaducungera atariyo yonyene, mugabo warabanejereje hamwe n’abavyeyi babo kugeza naho bibagira ubu butumwa bwawe nukuba mu bantu bahonejwe"
  25,19,"Ntankeka barabahakanye kubijanye nivyo mwavuze kandi ntimuzo shobora kwikurako ibihano canke kuronka imfashanyo, n’uwuzogira inabi iyariyo yose muri mwebwe tuzo muhonjesha ibihano bininiya cane"
  25,20,"Kandi ntitwarungitse imbere yawe intumwa z’Imana atari uko atamakenga arimwo kuko bahora bafungura ibifungurwa nukugenda mumasoko gusuma, kandi twarabahezagiye bamwe muri mwebwe ngo babe ibigeragezo kubandi, mbega muzo kwihangana? N’umuremyi wawe niwe abibona"